Now, to calculate the $\mathrm{NPV}$ for the lessee! let's remember that we must use the following formula:

$$
\begin{equation}
\mathrm{NPV}=R_{0}+\sum_{t=1}^{4} \frac{R_{t}}{(1+i)^{t}}
\end{equation}
$$

Where:

$R_0$: Cost of the asset,

$R_t$: Annual cash flows,

$i$: After-tax rate, and;

$t$: the number of years of life.
